			<div class="content" id="post-content-4446566">
									

<p>Welcome one and all to <strong>The Eternal MxTape</strong>! I'm having a lot of fun writing this story, and I hope you enjoy.</p>
<p>Many thanks to everyone who has helped out with draft critique, including <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kinchtheknifeblade" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1345012); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1345012&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1576363961" alt="kinchtheknifeblade" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1345012)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kinchtheknifeblade" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1345012); return false;">kinchtheknifeblade</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cybersqyd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5336470); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5336470&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1576363961" alt="cybersqyd" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5336470)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cybersqyd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5336470); return false;">cybersqyd</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255688); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255688&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1576363961" alt="DrAkimoto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255688); return false;">DrAkimoto</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/natvoltaic" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2800867); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2800867&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1576363961" alt="NatVoltaic" style="background-image:url(http://www.wi