			<div class="content" id="post-content-4446679">
									

<p>Gosh, thank you! I've been reading the SCP Wiki on and off for a few years before I thought of anything worth sharing. I've been writing fiction for a while (largely for horror RPG groups), but this is the first time I've shared something on this scale! It's certainly the first time I've tried something so experimental, and I understand if the &quot;alternate paths&quot; gimmick doesn't appeal to everyone. (In fact, I wrote &quot;Smile!&quot; before coming up with the theme&#8230; <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">I should probably give it another go-over, for clarity's sake.</span>) <strong>Edit</strong>: I've gone back and revised &quot;Smile!&quot; to include more context on the cassette's anomalous traits. Hopefully it's clearer now!</p>

